[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **What's wrong:** Nothing. The S3 key `f"documents/pubmed/batch-{timestamp}.xml"` has no leading slash. Correct.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
